@startuml Sequencia
autonumber
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Diagrama de Sequência — Pipeline via GrafoGen

actor "Pesquisador" as User
participant "GrafoGen\n(React)" as UI
participant "Express API\n:3001" as API
participant "main.py\n(Python)" as Py
participant "F1 Mining" as F1
participant "F3 Builders" as F3
participant "F4 Analysis" as F4
participant "GitHub API" as GH
database "data/raw/" as Raw
database "output/graphs/" as Gexf
database "output/reports/" as Rep

== Consultar status inicial ==

User -> UI : Abre Home
UI -> API : GET /api/status
API -> Raw : verifica CSVs
API -> Gexf : verifica .gexf
API -> Rep : verifica relatórios
API --> UI : stage1/2/3Complete,\ncontagens

== Etapa 1 — Mineração (opcional) ==

User -> UI : Executar Mineração
UI -> API : POST /api/pipeline/mine
API -> Py : spawn --mine
Py -> F1 : run_mining()
F1 -> GH : issues, PRs, reviews...
GH --> F1 : JSON paginado
F1 --> Py : Interaction[]
Py -> Raw : users.csv\ninteractions.csv\nevents.csv
Py --> API : exit 0
API --> UI : logs via polling /status

== Etapa 2 — Construção dos grafos ==

User -> UI : Executar Build
UI -> API : POST /api/pipeline/build
API -> Py : spawn --build
Py -> F3 : Graph1..4Builder.build()
F3 -> Raw : lê CSVs
F3 -> Gexf : export GEXF 1.3
Py --> API : exit 0
API --> UI : cards G1–G4 disponíveis

== Etapa 3 — Análise ==

User -> UI : Executar Análise
UI -> API : POST /api/pipeline/analyze
API -> Py : spawn --analyze
Py -> F3 : rebuild grafos em memória
Py -> F4 : centralidade,\nestrutura, Louvain
F4 -> Rep : centrality.csv\nstructure.json\ncommunities.csv
Py --> API : exit 0

== Visualização ==

User -> UI : Clica card G1
UI -> API : GET /api/graphs/G1
API -> Gexf : lê graph1_comments.gexf
API --> UI : XML GEXF
UI -> UI : gexfParser → Vis-Network

opt Métricas disponíveis
  UI -> API : GET /api/reports/centrality.csv
  API -> Rep : leitura
  API --> UI : CSV
  UI -> UI : MetricsPanel top 10
end

@enduml
